mayn m- mayn mogn iz geven in gantsn hoyl,

00:24:46.851 --> 00:24:51.303
un ikh hob gefunen a pudele, azoy klug bin ikh geven nisht tsu dertseyln, vi klug,

00:24:51.303 --> 00:24:53.361
ikh hob gekent shtarbn fun dem,

00:24:53.361 --> 00:24:58.353
hob ikh ge- gegangen un genumen dos pudele un ikh bin tsugegangen tsu a kikh gegangen melkn a bisl milkh.

00:24:58.596 --> 00:25:00.581
un dos hob ikh nisht getort ton.

00:25:01.465 --> 00:25:03.512
koydem iz geven a shmutsik pudele,

00:25:03.512 --> 00:25:06.807
un dos ts- un dos tsveyte,

00:25:07.270 --> 00:25:09.882
ikh hob nisht getort hobn keyn milkh, milkh iz geven fet,

00:25:09.882 --> 00:25:12.680
tsu fet far mayn mogn.

00:25:12.703 --> 00:25:14.891
un ikh hob oysgetrunken a bisl.

00:25:15.640 --> 00:25:17.822
un mir hot gehat veytikn

00:25:17.822 --> 00:25:21.467
ikh hob gezogt ikh vil shoyn shtarbn, ikh hob gezogt tsu mayn bruder, ikh gey aroys.

00:25:21.467 --> 00:25:22.906
ikh gey aroys.

00:25:23.925 --> 00:25:29.353
ni- iz er hot mir gehaltn, "gey nisht un gey nisht." un ikh hob gezogt, "ikh gey, zol men mir shisn.

00:25:30.051 --> 00:25:31.665
ikh vil nisht lebn shoyn."

00:25:31.992 --> 00:25:34.753
ikh hob im nisht gefolgt, ikh bin aroysgegangen,

00:25:35.029 --> 00:25:36.660
azoy vi in der vald bald,

00:25:36.767 --> 00:25:39.497
ikh bin tsugegangen tsum vald,

00:25:39.497 --> 00:25:41.688
tsum tsu a groysn boym,

00:25:41.863 --> 00:25:43.511
un ikh shpar mir on,

00:25:44.226 --> 00:25:47.766
ikh bin dokh azoy gelegn gelegn, un ikh shpar mir on, ikh halt dem boym,

00:25:47.766 --> 00:25:48.775
azoy o,

00:25:49.390 --> 00:25:50.582
un ikh hit,

00:25:50.892 --> 00:25:54.733
un ikh veys nisht vos ikh zol ton. un do geyen arum beheymes mit ferd,

00:25:55.077 --> 00:25:57.180
un ikh ze keynem nisht.

00:25:57.861 --> 00:26:03.592
azoy vi fun himl hot geton mir a ringl arum,

00:26:03.733 --> 00:26:05.856
azoy fil militer

00:26:05.856 --> 00:26:07.642
az ikh bin gevorn dershrokn.

00:26:07.733 --> 00:26:08.824
militer.

00:26:10.281 --> 00:26:13.160
trakht ikh mir, a vosara militer iz dos?

00:26:16.153 --> 00:26:19.437
ikh gib a kuk, zey hobn di royt, oy, zog ikh, efsher iz dos rusn.

00:26:19.478 --> 00:26:22.225
un m'tut a kum tsu tsu mir, ongehongen mit

00:26:22.225 --> 00:26:26.019
farshidene gevern, mit mit lopetes, ikh veys vos,

00:26:27.409 --> 00:26:27.878
yo.
